information: The company ATALAY CONSULT GESELLSCHAFT FÜR FORSTINVENTUR, TECHNOLOGIE UND SOFTWAREENTWICKLUNG GMBH, is a Service Provider, founded in 2000, which operates in the Crop services industry. It also operates in the Logging industries. It is based in Balve, Germany.
